This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) as it deals with the challenge of learning in the presence of label noise. It could also belong to the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV) as it applies to image classification tasks. Additionally, it could belong to the sub-category of natural language processing (cs.CL) as it applies to text classification tasks. Finally, it could belong to the sub-category of cryptography and security (cs.CR) as it deals with the issue of mislabeled datasets.
